flowchart TD
  A[Intake Draft task exists in DRAFT] --> B[PM creates structured Execution Contract draft]
  B --> C[Task history records task.execution_contract_version_recorded]
  C --> D[Reviewer routing policy selects Architect UX QA SRE Principal]
  D --> E{Section owner review complete?}
  E -->|No| F[Persist reviewer contribution through versioned section review]
  F --> C
  E -->|Blocking question open| G[Decision cluster remains blocking]
  G --> F
  E -->|Yes| H[PM validates and generates review Markdown]
  H --> I{Operator approval gate}
  I -->|Missing approvals or blocking questions| G
  I -->|Low-risk Simple auto approval eligible| J[Policy records Operator Approval]
  I -->|Explicit approval| K[Operator commits current version]
  J --> L[Generate verification skeleton when required]
  K --> L
  L --> M[Generate and approve reviewable artifact bundle]
  M --> N{Latest version still approved?}
  N -->|Yes| O[Implementation dispatch readiness true]
  N -->|Material change after approval| C
